org.sxb.session.web.http

インタフェース MultiHttpSessionStrategy

  • すべてのスーパーインタフェース:
    HttpSessionStrategy, RequestResponsePostProcessor
    既知の実装クラスのリスト:
    CookieHttpSessionStrategy

    public interface MultiHttpSessionStrategy
extends HttpSessionStrategy, RequestResponsePostProcessor

    Some HttpSessionStrategy may also want to further customize HttpServletRequest and HttpServletResponse objects. For example, CookieHttpSessionStrategy customizes how URL rewriting is done to select which session should be used in the event multiple sessions are active.

    導入されたバージョン:
    1.0
    作成者:
    Jeffson
    関連項目:
    CookieHttpSessionStrategy
